               <item n="m_passage_old">Act 12 and 13</item>
               <item n="m_philcomment_old">&lt;p&gt;This fragment contains the end of the twelfth and the beginning of the thirteenth act of the Maitreyasamitināṭaka. The colophon of act 12 is contained in line a1, act 13 begins in line a2f. An Uy. parallel to the latter is MaitrHami 13, 1a5-2a11. See also [[Pinault 1999]]: 200-201.&lt;/p&gt;</item>
